body_html: Can you try using https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/tools/benchmark and let me know what you get? There are some known optimizations for eight-bit CPU we're working on, but it would be useful to see where the time is going from the profiling logs you'll get from that tool.
